{"detail":"空间下载失败: (psycopg2.errors.InternalError_) ST_Intersects: Operation on mixed SRID geometries (Polygon, 4326) != (Polygon, 7030)\n\n[SQL: \n            SELECT * FROM geo_assets \n            WHERE ST_Intersects(\n                extent, \n                ST_MakeEnvelope(%(minX)s, %(minY)s, %(maxX)s, %(maxY)s, %(srid)s)\n            )\n        ]\n[parameters: {'minX': 12958824.0, 'minY': 4861223.0, 'maxX': 12959685.0, 'maxY': 4861984.0, 'srid': 7030}]\n(Background on this error at: https://sqlalche.me/e/20/2j85)"}